  "body": "# Rationale\r\n\r\n\"snapshot prune-state\" in testing takes additional disk space while it is running.\r\n\r\nUsers may prune because they are low on space, and running out during prune might worsen the situation. Maybe even up to DB corruption, going by initial reports.\r\n\r\n# Implementation\r\n\r\nTest for a safe amount of free space, and refuse to run if sufficient space is not present.\r\nBonus: Output a WARN log if free disk space is at or under N GiB, with N close to but over minimum needed free space, to be careful with space usage until prune has completed.\r\n",
